name: Nana Tanuki
description: Nana Yōkai Collection is a series of illustrations, created with the aim of sharing traditional Japanese mythology. In this series, Nana will be personifying herself as different Yōkai (Japanese spirits). Tanuki is not a Yokai itself is a raccoon dog but Tanuki is part of Japanese folklore. Tanuki is usually depicted with a hat, a bottle of sake that represents virtue, and huge testicles symbolizing economic luck.
